      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shares-mexicos-elektra-regain-ground-erasing-fraction-earlier-losses-2024-12-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥零售商 Grupo Elektra 股价周五上涨近 20%，抹去了一周累积的部分损失。]]></description>
