      <title>法国农业信贷银行在与意大利联合信贷银行的对决中增持 BPM 银行股份</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/credit-agricole-hikes-banco-bpm-holding-targets-1999-stake-2024-12-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，法国农业信贷银行在对意大利 BPM 银行的收购战中加大了赌注，利用衍生品增持了这家米兰银行的持股，目前该银行已成为意大利联合信贷银行的收购目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/credit-agricole-hikes-banco-bpm-holding-targets-1999-stake-2024-12-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 18:44:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦警告不要削弱金融风险监管机构</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-warns-against-weakening-financial-risk-watchdog-2024-12-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特耶伦周五警告称，由于人们越来越担心当选总统唐纳德特朗普的政府将再次削弱该机构，负责监控金融风险的委员会能够继续开展工作“至关重要”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-warns-against-weakening-financial-risk-watchdog-2024-12-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 18:10:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
